title: Dodgers' Ethier yells at Mattingly in dugout (Yahoo Sports)
text: Posts: 54,297 Dodgers' Ethier yells at Mattingly in dugout (Yahoo Sports) LOS ANGELES (AP) -- Los Angeles Dodgers right fielder Andre Ethier got into a shouting match with manager Don Mattingly in the bottom of the third inning of Game 5 of the NL Division Series.
